(96, 18, 'Share template HTML website bán hàng đơn giản', '<p>Ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c bạn! L&acirc;u rồi kh&ocirc;ng share g&igrave; cho anh em vọc vạch :D. H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh vừa code xong template n&agrave;y thấy kh&aacute; đẹp n&ecirc;n quyết định share cho anh em mang về d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mẫu HTML website b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng n&agrave;y ph&ugrave; hợp cho anh em n&agrave;o mang về để l&ecirc;n giao diện wordpress hoặc c&oacute; template sẳn để r&aacute;p backend. Ph&ugrave; hợp cho c&aacute;c bạn sinh vi&ecirc;n l&agrave;m đồ &aacute;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"280\" id=\"aswift_1\" name=\"aswift_1\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-1228209458646183&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6003256986&amp;adk=2839605868&amp;adf=1873879116&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6003256986&amp;w=730&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1671510181&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=730x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fhocwordpress.vn%2Fshare-template-html-website-ban-hang-don-gian&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTA4LjAuNTM1OS4xMjUiLFtdLGZhbHNlLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJOb3Q_QV9CcmFuZCIsIjguMC4wLjAiXSxbIkNocm9taXVtIiwiMTA4LjAuNTM1OS4xMjUiXSxbIkdvb2dsZSBDaHJvbWUiLCIxMDguMC41MzU5LjEyNSJdXSxmYWxzZV0.&amp;dt=1671510179751&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=246&amp;idt=1511&amp;shv=r20221207&amp;mjsv=m202212010101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3Dc03d2f6e11d6b68c-220db86419d90017%3AT%3D1671074597%3ART%3D1671074597%3AS%3DALNI_MbutSD7aumHR4tp8xlYTqHiyvSVtA&amp;gpic=UID%3D00000b90e8ce2665%3AT%3D1671074597%3ART%3D1671499453%3AS%3DALNI_Mai3DpJPgDWdcEguDpq3-Dpnq7APQ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5474012362780&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;ga_vid=1838415590.1670814841&amp;ga_sid=1671510181&amp;ga_hid=470784589&amp;ga_fc=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=19&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=768&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=0.9&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=194&amp;ady=560&